* Iron Raptor scanned down each of the pipes, the one to her left led to the 
storage area, the one to her right eventually led to a control console. She 
looked over her shoulder then continued down the right pipe, there was 
mostly more value in a computer program then a 36 gauge phaser.
Iron Raptor stopped when she came to a grating that emptied out into a large 
room...BINGO!
Computers lined the wall to the front and left, a two doored entrance was to 
the right.
Iron Raptor opened her comlink to the Coded frequency...*

" Liono, I'm inside of the Predacon base. I'm at the entrance to a computer 
control room, if there's anything that you need me to get say it now before 
I strip the place."
